org.sbolstandard.core

Interface SBOLRootObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SBOLObject, SBOLVisitable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Collection, DnaComponent, DnaSequence
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectionImpl, DnaComponentImpl, DnaSequenceImpl
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface SBOLRootObject
extends SBOLObject
    Marker interface to denote which SBOL objects can be added directly to an SBOLDocument as top-level objects. Some objects such as SequenceAnnotations cannot be top-level objects, thus dos not implement this interface.

    Evren Sirin
